overview.en: UTI Chain Ecology aims to build a distributed business engine through blockchain technology. While constructing three major service systems, it uses blockchain services, namely BaaS, and four-dimensional integration to establish a cloud computing platform that combines centralization and decentralization. Create an efficient, high-speed, intelligent, trusted, reliable, and controllable super cloud.
overview.zh: 尤泰链生态旨在通过区块链技术打造分布式商业引擎，在构建三大服务体系同时，利用区块链服务即BaaS，四维一体，建立中心化与去中心化相结合的云计算平台，打造高效、高速、智能又可信、可靠、可控制的超级云。
